{"tid":1103216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消委會就美容及健身中心合約冷靜期提意見","createTime":"2019-04-12T09:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T06:10:37.000Z","uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd8a930137bc85e7b1bf74cba0d5201a2ffb6ff","tid":1103216,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T09:07:29.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府就美容及健身中心消費合約設冷靜期公眾諮詢下周二屆滿，消委會向政府提交意見。<br />\n<br />\n消委會支持7日冷靜期及14日退款期的建議，認為可令消費者有足夠時間思考，並同意現階段不加入時光共享旅遊會籍，因只集中少數經營者及未成趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n消委會建議主體法例框架外同時引入附屬法例，日後如其他行業出現威嚇及不良銷售手法，可以較便捷將其納入適用範圍，預繳金額亦應納入附屬法例，強調草擬法例要有彈性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=344288\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D344288&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8LHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=404b8b6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D344288&h=54cfef26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=344288</a>"},{"pid":"829396f50cae45c69a8fd999ef69bcdf858f6791","tid":1103216,"uid":7828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T09:08:10.000Z","msg":"美容：<br />\n雅蘭15樓<br />\n佐敦新貿中心14樓<br />\n銅鑼灣世貿22樓<br />\n<br />\n教育：<br />\n英文：信和9樓<br />\nPlaygroup: 太子柏宜7-9樓<br />\n投資：潮特4-5樓"},{"pid":"8c372e904d1eb778efdc07ee3731a06fe44c1842","tid":1103216,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"健身：羅素街"},{"pid":"b780cb370d5b56d83d4f19ff5059db2a208c0537","tid":1103216,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T23:21:58.000Z","msg":"幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴晚比人夾住去比錢<br />\n今日想上去嘈"},{"pid":"bec44b1c8c66584d1bac947eb08be84513fe7f0f","tid":1103216,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T23:39:23.000Z"